---
const steps = [
  {
    title: 'Choose Your Challenge',
    description:
      'Choose from a variety of challenges, each with a different design and difficulty level. The challenges are designed to both test your HTML and CSS skills, and to help you develop a keen eye for detail.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Spot the Difference',
    description:
      "Use your keen eye for detail to identify the inconsistencies between the two designs. Is it a color that's off? Maybe the padding isn't quite right, or perhaps an element is misaligned. The devil is in the detail!",
  },
  {
    title: 'Correct the Code',
    description:
      "You're given the existing code for the incorrect design. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to dive into the HTML and CSS and fix the issues. Your changes will update the design in real time, so you can see the effect of your code adjustments.",
  },
  {
    title: 'Achieve PixelPerfection',
    description:
      "Keep refining until you can't tell the difference between the two designs. Use the comparison tool to get your rating and see the designs overlayed. Voila, you've achieved PixelPerfection!",
  },
  {
    title: 'Level Up',
    description:
      'Complete challenges to earn experience points (XP). The faster and more accurately you solve them, the more XP you earn. Track your progress, climb the leaderboard, and become a PixelPerfection champion!',
  },
]
---

<div
  class='w-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-white to-[200px] dark:to-gray-800 pb-24 flex flex-col items-center justify-center'
>
  <ul class='text-left mt-[100px]'>
    {
      steps.map(({ title, description }, index) => (
        <li class='flex gap-2 mb-4 w-full px-2 mx-auto max-w-screen-md'>
          <div class='flex flex-col w-16 items-center'>
            <div class='w-16 h-16 font-lato text-4xl text-gray-700 dark:text-white relative flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4'>
              <span>{index + 1}</span>
            </div>
            <div class='w-[4px] h-full bg-gray-700 dark:bg-white' />
          </div>
          <div class='pb-12 px-6'>
            <h3 class='font-bold text-2xl text-blue-500'>{title}</h3>
            <p class='text-xl'>{description}</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))
    }
  </ul>

  <a
    href='/app'
    class='bg-blue-500 text-2xl hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-full'
    >Let's perfect some pixels!</a
  >
</div>
